{"tid":1655664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國男子涉嘉頓山傷人　被控4項企圖謀殺罪","createTime":"2019-10-15T07:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T08:28:57.000Z","uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5eadb173ac6c96c82642f06e91c4e32623e60a","tid":1655664,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:35:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486288-20191015.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486288-20191015.htm&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9OSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=66c76a15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486288-20191015.htm&h=91b72209\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486288-20191015.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n一名中國男子涉嫌與日前深水埗嘉頓山傷人案有關，他被暫控4項「企圖謀殺」罪，下午在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n該名男子涉嫌在上星期五於嘉頓山懷疑以一把6吋長的生果刀，襲擊4名正在做運動的女子，其後逃去，原因不明，4名事主受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n警方進一步調查後，前日在深圳灣口岸拘捕一名24歲中國男子。"},{"pid":"ff1271fa8e26db3b71f9d67e9aaa42e1759e818a","tid":1655664,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:36:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b7cf60bebd9b67046f8ad4dee196ad86ed20a2e","tid":1655664,"uid":43657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"流浮山刀手？"},{"pid":"3634d13030c7674f882d84430dacb753de83001c","tid":1655664,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"Cls 係咪精神病"},{"pid":"f41754fa9699920f179ac5c1e7e01ad37d05737f","tid":1655664,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:28:57.000Z","msg":"是咪因為大媽舞太嘈?"}]}